      dct:source narr:Sample_ResearchBranchMethodology_20260408 ;
      skos:note "The document opens and closes with explicit provisional framing ('Provisional — from research/goal-directed-agents exploration branch, not yet promoted to main'). This meta-register — a document that announces its own epistemic status — is a distinctive stylistic feature of the research branch methodology. The provisional flag is both content and form." ;
      rdf:value true ;
